# Project Management Guidelines

## Tools
- ALWAYS use `uv` commands for all workspace and package management operations, unless there is no equivalent `uv` command.
    - Editing a `pyproject.toml` file
    - Adding dependencies to a package
    - Removing dependencies from a package
    - Syncing the workspace
    - Running package commands
    - Running tests

## Constitution
- The [constitution](.specify/memory/constitution.md) is the source of truth for the project.
- You must follow the constitution at all times.
